{"tid":1942583,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 美國參議院與政府已就經濟刺激法案達成一致意見","createTime":"2020-03-25T07:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T16:07:03.000Z","uid":3302,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"943508c6e3187b47566bb40a5949b65846771c26","tid":1942583,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"外電引述美國白宮一名官員透露，參議院與政府為應對新型冠狀病毒疫情推動的2萬億美元經濟刺激法案，已經達成一致意見。<br />\n<br />\n參議院共和黨領袖麥康奈爾亦表示，今晚稍後將對法案進行投票。協議文本預計稍後公布。<br />\n<br />\n外界預期，方案包括一筆5000億美元資金，用於協助受創行業，另外一筆規模相近資金將用於向數以百萬計美國家庭，直接派發最多3000美元。法案亦包括2500億美元基金，用於擴大失業援助，以及750億美元資金用於醫療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516729-20200325.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516729-20200325.htm&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=cd070e61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516729-20200325.htm&h=a449410e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516729-20200325.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f03102e20af97368b9ec262965587c88aa19d130","tid":1942583,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"救市方案準備通過<br />\n唔夠錢塞到你夠為止<br />\n總之唔準破產炒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20afbd55ea819623e05b490300a56eb359363510","tid":1942583,"uid":122906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"唔知眾議院點諗"},{"pid":"22e7019feff60fc5192496da2a0a4863c938d51f","tid":1942583,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"20afbd55ea819623e05b490300a56eb359363510","tid":1942583,"uid":122906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"唔知眾議院點諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"共和黨控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b3a15bda9bbf407951a217e7fa4a73be01509e","tid":1942583,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"美國白宮與國會就緊急經濟刺激計劃達協議。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮官員Eric Ueland稱，參議院和特朗普政府官員已就一項大規模經濟刺激法案達成協議，以減輕新冠病毒疫情對經濟的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經過數日談判後達成的這項刺激計劃規模預計達到2萬億美元。<br />\n<br />\n參議院共和黨領袖麥康奈爾稱，周三稍晚將對新冠疫情經濟刺激法案進行投票。<br />\n<br />\n該協議的文本預計要到周三晚些時候才能公布。<br />\n<br />\n外界原先預期，這套方案將包括一筆5000億美元的資金，用於協助受創的行業，另外一筆規模相近的資金將用於直接支付最多達3000美元給美國數以百萬計的每個家庭，同時還有一筆2500億美元的基金用於擴大失業救助，另有750億美元資金用於醫院。<br />\n<br />\n今日投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b76874d34880b9380d5ff22bca8a6ba643a4129","tid":1942583,"uid":4258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"救市可以無限印錢但public healthcare 就話無錢搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a6c82a86d7c06a04d701f3a8ba8040c028d903","tid":1942583,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"華爾街又可以炒爆cap水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843c8bafcfae33bfd17964b11841a6a7fac84738","tid":1942583,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uT9BWG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuT9BWG8.png&h=3f6b2b85&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一個月既反彈浪黎料<br />\n有貨既好準備蝕少少走佬 唔好話冇提你<br />\n最後逃生門"},{"pid":"70fa1af6fb80afc5bf777821f2ceb589a40ef8be","tid":1942583,"uid":11556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e7019feff60fc5192496da2a0a4863c938d51f","tid":1942583,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"20afbd55ea819623e05b490300a56eb359363510","tid":1942583,"uid":122906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:13:01.000Z","msg